            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(128,128,128,0.2); padding-top: 15px;">
                <button type="button" id="btn-copy-app" onclick="copyAppearanceSettings()" style="width:100%; padding: 6px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(128,128,128,0.3); color: inherit; transition: background 0.2s; margin-bottom: 0;">📋 Copy to Clipboard</button>To safeguard your settings as you make edits, use button above to copy current settings. You can then paste them into User Notes for safekeeping. Don't forget to Save Settings before making changes.
                <button type="button" onclick="resetAppearanceDefaults()" style="width:100%; padding: 6px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; background: rgba(255,68,68,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,68,68,0.3); color: #ff5555; transition: background 0.2s;">⚠️ Set to Defaults</button>
            </div>
            
        </div>


            <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #cbcbcb; border-radius: 8px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 5px;">Custom CSS</h3>
                <p style="margin-top: 2px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px;">Override standard appearance. E.g., <code>.qf-row { background-color: #999 !important; }</code></p>
                <textarea name="custom_css" style="flex-grow: 1; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: monospace; padding: 10px; background: #111; color: #0f0; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 4px; resize: none;"><?= htmlspecialchars($saved_css) ?></textarea>
            </div>

            <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;">
        
				<div class="qf-guide-block">
                    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">Advanced Icon Guide</h3>
                    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px;">The auto-scanner tries to find native Unraid icons, but you have three powerful ways to customize them manually:</p>

                    <h4 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px;">1. Google Noto Emojis (Recommended)</h4>
                    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5;">
                        You can use standard emojis, and the plugin will automatically upgrade them to the high-quality <strong>Google Noto Color</strong> style. This ensures consistent, premium 3D-style icons across all devices (Windows, Mac, iOS, Android).
                    </p>
                    <ul style="margin-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong>Quick Pick:</strong> Press <code>Win + .</code> (Windows) or <code>Cmd + Ctrl + Space</code> (Mac) to open your OS emoji keyboard and insert directly.</li>
                        <li><strong>Browse online:</strong> Visit <a href="https://emojiterra.com/" target="_blank" style="color: #4da6ff; text-decoration: none;">emojiterra.com</a> to browse icons. You will see how the emoji looks on different platforms (Apple, Google, etc.). Simply click "Copy" on the raw Unicode character and paste it here. <br><em>Note: Even if it temporarily looks like the standard Windows/Mac flat emoji when you paste it into the box, the plugin will automatically transform it into the beautiful Google version in the live preview and final menu!</em></li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px;">2. FontAwesome & Custom Images</h4>
                    <ul style="margin-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 0;">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><strong>FontAwesome:</strong> Type any FA class (e.g., <code>fa-desktop</code>).</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><strong>Images:</strong> Paste the full path to a PNG/SVG (e.g., <code>/plugins/name/icon.png</code>).</li>
                        <li><strong>Inspect Element:</strong> You can right-click any native Unraid header icon, click <strong>Inspect</strong>, and copy either its <code>fa-</code> class or image <code>src</code> path.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>



                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1;">
                    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 16px;">User Notes</h3>
                    <textarea name="user_notes" class="qf-notes-area" style="resize: none; font-size: 12px;" placeholder="Save snippets or script arguments..."><?= htmlspecialchars($saved_notes) ?></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </form>



<script>


$(function() {
    // 1. Drag and Drop Sorting
    if (typeof $.fn.sortable !== 'undefined') {
        $("#fav-table-body").sortable({
            handle: '.drag-handle',
            cursor: 'grabbing',
            axis: 'y',
            opacity: 0.8
        });
    }

    // 2. Bulletproof Hybrid Color Picker Sync
    // When the color box changes...
    $(document).on('input change', '.color-picker-sync', function() {
        var hex = $(this).val().toUpperCase();
        $(this).siblings('.color-text-sync').val(hex);
    });
    
    // When the text box changes...
    $(document).on('input keyup', '.color-text-sync', function() {
        var hex = $(this).val().trim();
        
        // Auto-add the # if the user forgets it
        if (hex.length > 0 && hex.charAt(0) !== '#') {
            hex = '#' + hex;
        }
        
        // Standard HTML color inputs require exactly 6 valid characters (plus the #)
        if(/^#[0-9A-F]{6}$/i.test(hex)) {
            $(this).siblings('.color-picker-sync').val(hex);
        }
    });
});

// 3. Table Functions (Preview & Fetch Icon)

function updatePreview(inputElement) {
    var val = $(inputElement).val().trim();
    var wrapper = $(inputElement).siblings('.preview-wrapper');
    
    // 1. Default (Star)
    if (val === '') {
        wrapper.html('<i class="fa fa-star" style="width:28px; text-align:center; font-size:24px;"></i>');
        return;
    }
    
    // 2. Images & URLs
    if (val.includes('/') || val.includes('.')) {
        wrapper.html('<img src="' + val + '" style="width:28px; height:28px; object-fit:contain;">');
        return;
    }
    
    // 3. Native Unraid FontAwesome 4 Format
    if (/^[a-zA-Z0-9\-\s]+$/.test(val)) {
        var cleanName = val.trim();
        
        // If the user typed "fa-" at the beginning, strip it off temporarily
        if (cleanName.startsWith('fa-')) {
            cleanName = cleanName.substring(3);
        }
        
        // Rebuild it to exactly match the Unraid core HTML you just inspected
        wrapper.html('<i class="fa fa-' + cleanName + '" style="width:28px; text-align:center; font-size:24px;"></i>');
        return;
    }
    
    // 4. Emojis
    wrapper.html('<span style="font-family: \'Noto Color Emoji\', sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px; display: inline-block; width: 28px; text-align: center;">' + val + '</span>');
}


function fetchNativeIcon(btnElement) {
    var row = $(btnElement).closest('tr');
    var path = row.find('.path-input').val().trim();
    var iconInput = row.find('input[name="icon[]"]');
    var wrapper = iconInput.siblings('.preview-wrapper');
    
    if (path === '') {
        alert("Please enter a path/URL first!");
        return;
    }

    wrapper.html('<i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin"></i>');
    
    $.post('/Settings/QuickFavorites', { action: 'get_native_icon', path: path }, function(response) {
        var finalIcon = response.trim();
        if (finalIcon === '' || finalIcon.includes('spin')) finalIcon = 'fa-star';
        iconInput.val(finalIcon);
        updatePreview(iconInput);
    }).fail(function() {
        iconInput.val('fa-star');
        updatePreview(iconInput);
    });
}

function addRow() {
    var newRow = `<tr class="qf-row">
        <td class="drag-handle" title="Drag to reorder"><i class="fa fa-bars"></i></td>
        <td style="max-width: 140px;"><input type="text" name="category[]" placeholder="Category" required class="qf-input"></td>
        <td style="max-width: 140px;"><input type="text" name="label[]" placeholder="Label" required class="qf-input"></td>
        <td><input type="text" name="path[]" placeholder="Folder or URL" required class="qf-input path-input"></td>
        <td>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;">
                <span class="preview-wrapper"><i class="fa fa-star"></i></span>
                <input type="text" name="icon[]" placeholder="fa-star" required class="qf-input" oninput="updatePreview(this)">
            </div>
        </td>
        <td>
		
			<select name="action_type[]" class="qf-input">
                <option value="_self">Same Tab</option>
                <option value="_blank">New Tab</option>
                <option value="script_modal">Run Script (Console)</option>
                <option value="script_background">Run Background</option>
                <option value="script_log">User Script Log</option>
            </select>

			
			
        </td>
        <td class="qf-row-right-end" style="text-align:center;">
            <button type="button" class="qf-btn-remove" onclick="$(this).closest('tr').remove();"><i class="fa fa-times"></i></button>
        </td>
    </tr>`;

$('#fav-table-body').append(newRow);
}

// 4. Appearance Backup & Reset Functions
function copyAppearanceSettings() {
    var text = "--- Theme Backup ---\n";
    text += "Header Title: " + $('input[name="menu_title"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Icon Size: " + $('input[name="icon_size"]').val() + "px\n";
    text += "Grid Columns: " + $('input[name="grid_columns"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Menu Width: " + $('input[name="menu_width"]').val() + "px\n";
    text += "Show Header: " + $('select[name="show_header"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Menu BG: " + $('input[name="bg_color"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Hover BG: " + $('input[name="hover_color"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Header Font: " + $('input[name="header_color"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Header Line: " + $('input[name="header_line"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Section Font: " + $('input[name="section_title_color"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Section Line: " + $('input[name="section_border_color"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Icon (FA): " + $('input[name="icon_color"]').val() + "\n";
    text += "Label Font: " + $('input[name="label_color"]').val();

    // Fallback method for local HTTP Unraid connections
    var tempTextArea = document.createElement("textarea");
    tempTextArea.value = text;
    // Move it off-screen so it doesn't cause a layout jump
    tempTextArea.style.position = "absolute";
    tempTextArea.style.left = "-9999px";
    document.body.appendChild(tempTextArea);
    tempTextArea.select();
    tempTextArea.setSelectionRange(0, 99999); // For mobile compatibility

    try {
        document.execCommand("copy");
        var btn = $('#btn-copy-app');
        var originalText = btn.html();
        btn.html('✅ Copied!');
        btn.css('background', 'rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1)');
        setTimeout(function() { 
            btn.html(originalText); 
            btn.css('background', 'rgba(255,255,255,0.08)');
        }, 2000);
    } catch (err) {
        alert("Clipboard copy failed. Your browser may be blocking it.");
    }

    // Clean up the invisible text area
    document.body.removeChild(tempTextArea);
}

function resetAppearanceDefaults() {
    swal({
        title: "Reset Appearance?",
        text: "This will reset all styling back to the default theme.\n\n(You will still need to click 'Save Settings' afterward to make it permanent.)",
        type: "warning",
        showCancelButton: true,
        confirmButtonColor: "#ff4444",
        confirmButtonText: "Yes, reset it!",
        closeOnConfirm: true
    }, function() {
        // Reset Standard Inputs
        $('input[name="menu_title"]').val('Quick Favorites');
        $('input[name="icon_size"]').val('32');
        $('input[name="grid_columns"]').val('4');
        $('input[name="menu_width"]').val('480');
        $('select[name="show_header"]').val('yes');

        // Helper function to reset both the text box and the color picker block safely
        function setCol(name, val) {
            var textInput = $('input[name="'+name+'"]');
            textInput.val(val.toUpperCase());
            textInput.siblings('.color-picker-sync').val(val);
        }

        // Reset Colors
        setCol('bg_color', '#1c1c1c');
        setCol('hover_color', '#333333');
        setCol('header_color', '#ffca28');
        setCol('header_line', '#333333');
        setCol('section_title_color', '#888888');
        setCol('section_border_color', '#333333');
        setCol('icon_color', '#e0e0e0');
        setCol('label_color', '#cccccc');
    });
}

</script>

]]>
</INLINE>
</FILE>

<FILE Name="/usr/local/emhttp/plugins/&name;/fav_overlay.page">
<INLINE>
<![CDATA[
<?php
$cfg_dir = "/boot/config/plugins/quick.favorites";
$json_file = "$cfg_dir/favorites.json";
$appearance_file = "$cfg_dir/appearance.json";

$grouped_favs = [];
if (file_exists($json_file)) {
    $raw = json_decode(file_get_contents($json_file), true);
    if (is_array($raw)) {
        foreach ($raw as $path => $data) {
            if (is_string($data)) $data = ['category' => 'General', 'label' => $data, 'icon' => 'fa-star', 'action' => '_self'];
            $cat = !empty($data['category']) ? $data['category'] : 'Uncategorized';
            $data['path'] = $path;
            $grouped_favs[$cat][] = $data;
        }
    }
}

$defaults = ['menu_title' => 'Quick Favorites', 'icon_size' => '32', 'bg_color' => '#1c1c1c', 'header_color' => '#ffca28', 'header_line' => '#333333', 'section_title_color' => '#888888', 'section_border_color' => '#333333', 'icon_color' => '#e0e0e0', 'label_color' => '#cccccc', 'grid_columns' => '4', 'menu_width' => '480', 'hover_color' => '#333333', 'show_header' => 'yes'];
$style = file_exists($appearance_file) ? array_merge($defaults, json_decode(file_get_contents($appearance_file), true)) : $defaults;
?>

<style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Color+Emoji&display=swap');
    #my-custom-fav-menu { display:none; position:absolute; z-index:99999; border:1px solid #444; border-radius:8px; box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); width: <?= $style['menu_width'] ?>px; padding: 10px 20px; background: <?= $style['bg_color'] ?> !important; box-sizing: border-box; }
    .qf-main-header { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px; padding-bottom: 8px; color: <?= $style['header_color'] ?> !important; border-bottom: 1px solid <?= $style['header_line'] ?> !important; <?= ($style['show_header'] === 'no') ? 'display:none;' : '' ?> }
    .qf-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(<?= $style['grid_columns'] ?>, 1fr); gap: 0px 0px; justify-items: center; }
    .qf-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding: 10px 5px; text-decoration: none !important; width: 100%; text-align: center; }
    .qf-item:hover { background: <?= $style['hover_color'] ?> !important; }
    .qf-icon-fa { font-size: <?= $style['icon_size'] ?>px !important; color: <?= $style['icon_color'] ?> !important; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .qf-icon-img { width: <?= $style['icon_size'] ?>px; height: <?= $style['icon_size'] ?>px; object-fit: contain; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .qf-label { font-size: 11px; color: <?= $style['label_color'] ?> !important; line-height: 1.2; word-wrap: break-word; }
</style>

<div id="my-custom-fav-menu">
    <div class="qf-main-header"><?= htmlspecialchars($style['menu_title']) ?></div>
    <?php if (empty($grouped_favs)): ?>
        <div style="color:#888; font-size:12px; padding:20px; text-align:center;">No links found in Settings</div>
    <?php else: ?>
        <?php foreach ($grouped_favs as $category => $items): ?>
            <div class="qf-section">
                <div class="qf-section-title" style="color:<?= $style['section_title_color'] ?>; border-bottom:1px solid <?= $style['section_border_color'] ?>; font-size:10px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:5px;"><?= htmlspecialchars($category) ?></div>
                <div class="qf-grid">
                    <?php foreach ($items as $item): 
                        $isScript = (strpos($item['action'], 'script') !== false);
                        $href = $isScript ? '#' : htmlspecialchars($item['path']);
                    ?>
                        <a href="<?= $href ?>" data-action="<?= $item['action'] ?>" data-path="<?= htmlspecialchars($item['path']) ?>" class="qf-item">
                            <?php if (strpos($item['icon'], '/') !== false || strpos($item['icon'], '.') !== false): ?>
                                <img src="<?= htmlspecialchars($item['icon']) ?>" class="qf-icon-img">
                            <?php elseif (preg_match('/^[a-zA-Z0-9\-]+$/', $item['icon'])): ?>
                                <i class="fa <?= (strpos($item['icon'], 'fa-') === 0) ? $item['icon'] : 'fa-'.$item['icon'] ?> qf-icon-fa"></i>
                            <?php else: ?>
                                <span style="font-family: 'Noto Color Emoji', sans-serif; font-size: <?= $style['icon_size'] ?>px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px;"><?= htmlspecialchars($item['icon']) ?></span>
                            <?php endif; ?>
                            <span class="qf-label"><?= htmlspecialchars($item['label']) ?></span>
                        </a>
                    <?php endforeach; ?>
                </div>
            </div>
        <?php endforeach; ?>
    <?php endif; ?>
</div>
]]>
</INLINE>
</FILE>

<FILE Name="/usr/local/emhttp/plugins/&name;/favs.js">
<INLINE>
<![CDATA[
// 1. DISARM UNRAID'S DEFAULT NAVIGATION
var favBtn = document.querySelector('a[href="/Favorites"]');
if (favBtn) {
    favBtn.removeAttribute('onclick');
}

// 2. YOUR CUSTOM CLICK LISTENER
document.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
    var clickedLink = e.target.closest('a[href="/Favorites"]');
    var customMenu = document.getElementById('my-custom-fav-menu');

    if (clickedLink) {
        e.preventDefault(); e.stopPropagation();
        if (!customMenu) return;

        if (customMenu.style.display === 'block') {
            customMenu.style.display = 'none';
        } else {
            customMenu.style.display = 'block';
            var rect = clickedLink.getBoundingClientRect();
            var menuWidth = customMenu.offsetWidth || 480;
            var btnCenter = rect.left + window.scrollX + (rect.width / 2);
            var calculatedLeft = Math.max(15, Math.min(btnCenter - (menuWidth / 2), window.innerWidth - menuWidth - 15));
            customMenu.style.top = (rect.bottom + window.scrollY + 10) + 'px';
            customMenu.style.left = calculatedLeft + 'px';
        }
    }
    else if (customMenu && customMenu.style.display === 'block') {
        if (!e.target.closest('#my-custom-fav-menu')) {
            customMenu.style.display = 'none';
        } else {
            var itemTarget = e.target.closest('.qf-item');
            if (itemTarget) {
                var action = itemTarget.getAttribute('data-action');
                var path = itemTarget.getAttribute('data-path').trim();
                var token = (typeof csrf_token !== 'undefined') ? csrf_token : '';

                if (action === '_blank') {
                    window.open(path, '_blank');
                    customMenu.style.display = 'none';
                } else if (action === '_self') {
                    window.location.href = path;
                } else if (action === 'script_modal') {
                    openTerminal('run_script', 'user.scripts', path);
                    customMenu.style.display = 'none';
                } else if (action === 'script_background') {
                    $.post('/plugins/user.scripts/exec.php', { action: 'background', script: path, csrf_token: token });
                    customMenu.style.display = 'none';
                } else if (action === 'script_log') {
                    // 1. Open a blank Unraid terminal window first
                    var logWin = window.open('', '_blank', 'width=800,height=600,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes');
                    
                    // Path updated to quick.favorites
                    $.post('/plugins/quick.favorites/log_api.php', { 
                        path: path, 
                        csrf_token: token 
                    }, function(logData) {
                        
                        var checkReady = setInterval(function() {
                            if (logWin && logWin.document && logWin.document.readyState === 'complete') {
                                clearInterval(checkReady);
                                
                                var contentDiv = logWin.document.createElement('div');
                                contentDiv.style.whiteSpace = 'pre-wrap';
                                contentDiv.style.marginBottom = '20px';
                                contentDiv.innerHTML = logData; 
                                
                                logWin.document.body.insertBefore(contentDiv, logWin.document.body.firstChild);
                                logWin.scrollTo(0, logWin.document.body.scrollHeight);
                            }
                        }, 50);
                    });
                    
                    customMenu.style.display = 'none';
                }
            }
        }
    }
}, true);
]]>
</INLINE>
</FILE>

<FILE Name="/usr/local/emhttp/plugins/&name;/log_api.php">
<INLINE>
<![CDATA[
<?php
// 1. SECURE SESSION & CSRF CHECK
@session_start();
$request_token = trim($_POST['csrf_token'] ?? '');
if (!isset($_SESSION['csrf_token']) || $request_token !== $_SESSION['csrf_token']) {
    die("Security Error: CSRF Token mismatch.");
}

// 2. PREVENT PATH TRAVERSAL
$path = trim($_POST['path'] ?? '');
$path = preg_replace('/[^a-zA-Z0-9 \-_]/', '', $path); // Only allow safe folder names

if (empty($path)) {
    die("Error: Invalid path provided.");
}

$logFile = "/tmp/user.scripts/tmpScripts/" . $path . "/log.txt";

if (file_exists($logFile)) {
    $logData = file_get_contents($logFile);
    
    // 3. XSS SANITIZATION (The "Carwash")
    // Allow colors/bolding but strip dangerous scripts
    $safeTags = '<b><i><u><strong><em><span><div><font><br><hr><p>';
    $logData = strip_tags($logData, $safeTags);
    
    // Rip out "onclick", "onerror", etc.
    $logData = preg_replace('/(?:\s+on[a-z]+\s*=\s*(?:(?:"[^"]*")|(?:\'[^\']*\')|[^>\s]+))/i', '', $logData);
    
    echo $logData;
} else {
    echo "Log file not found for: " . htmlspecialchars($path);
}
?>


]]>
</INLINE>
</FILE>

